# ERP code quality & structure

Follow `.cursor/rules/erp-project-structure.mdc` layers **without exception**. This rule adds the quality bar.

## Structure non-negotiables

- **One API route per module** (`/api/sales`, `/api/procurement`, `/api/inventory`) ‚Äî extend with `resource` param, never add parallel routes for the same domain  
- **Business logic in `src/lib/server/`** ‚Äî never in `page.tsx` or route handlers beyond auth + dispatch  
- **Shared UI** in `src/components/modules/*-shared.tsx` (columns, headers) ‚Äî not copy-pasted per page  
- **Cross-module concerns** in dedicated libs (`src/lib/documents/`, `src/lib/sales/below-cost.ts`, etc.)  
- **Types** in `src/lib/types/index.ts` until split is justified (>300 lines in types file)  

## Before finishing a task

1. `pnpm exec tsc --noEmit` ‚Äî fix type errors  
2. Match naming/style of the nearest completed module (Sales ‚Üí Procurement ‚Üí Inventory)  
3. Wire UI end-to-end: list ‚Üí dialog ‚Üí `lib/data` ‚Üí API ‚Üí server ‚Üí migration (if needed)  
4. Run docs sync per `erp-docs-and-features.mdc`  

## Optional / admin features

- **Every new user-facing capability** must ship with a `feat_*` flag ‚Äî see checklist below
- Add `feat_*` in `feature-flags.ts` + `featureFlagDefs` + admin toggle on Feature Management (`/admin/features`)
- Server must respect flag via `isCompanyFeatureEnabled` when API behavior changes (do not rely on UI-only hiding)
- Per-company settings ‚Üí migration + `src/app/api/admin/...` + admin page section

### New feature checklist (mandatory)

1. `src/lib/mock-data/feature-flags.ts` ‚Äî `key`, `label`, `description`, `category`
2. `src/lib/feature-flags.ts` ‚Äî add to `BUSINESS_LINE_MODULE_FLAGS` (on by default) or `OPTIONAL_FEATURE_FLAGS` (off by default)
3. Export flag constant from domain lib (e.g. `PRODUCT_WAREHOUSE_AVAILABILITY_FLAG` in `lib/sales/`)
4. UI: `useAppStore((s) => s.isFeatureEnabled(FLAG))` before showing behavior
5. Server (if API changes): `isCompanyFeatureEnabled(db, companyId, FLAG)` in `lib/server/`
6. Docs: `PROGRESS_INDEX.md` ¬ß3, `docs/EXTRA_FEATURES.md`, `01_BUILD_PROMPT.md` appendix

## File size & clarity

- Split files approaching **500 lines**  
- No duplicate totals/calculations ‚Äî use `src/lib/sales/calculations.ts`  
- Comments only for non-obvious business rules (VAT, UAE compliance, approval flows)  

